<front>
<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Dietrich Hofer von Lobenstein, Pfleger zu Straubing</head><p>Makulierter Entwurf des folgenden Briefs.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_64" id="30v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l1"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hofer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l2">Pfleger cʒu <expan>Strawbing<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l3">Lieber her Pfleger / vns hat der Edel wolgeporen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Graf </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l5">Ecʒel von Ortemberg 
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l4">vnd vicʒtum in nydern Beyern </ab></add> vormals 
<del rend="strikethrough">e</del> eınen brief geſant vnd <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l6">von <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Caſpar hertembergers wegen / darauff wir Jm wider </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l7"><expan>geſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geantvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / als wir euch abſchrift ſenden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l8">verſloſſen in diſem brief / Nu iſt vns biʒ her noch khein <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l10">darauff woꝛden 
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1576657658232_4106">ſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1576657660627_4111">vvıe das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1576657662499_4116">der </ab></add> <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> graf </del></ab><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1576657667074_4126">Graf Ecʒel 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒu der </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1576657664602_4121">lange </ab></add> </ab><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1576657669707_4131">
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒeit </del> niht anheim ſeẏ </ab><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1576657672229_4136">gevveſen </ab></add> / vnd alſo wiſſen wir niht / vvie wir mit <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l14"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Caſpar<ex>en</ex></expan> hertemberg daran ſein / <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l11">wen<ex>n</ex>
<del rend="strikethrough"> Sey eʒ daʒ </del> der
<del><expan>ſ<ex>elbe</ex></expan></del> vicʒtum <expan>heimkume<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l12">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſey </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l17">willen / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Caſpar daran weẏſen wöllet / daʒ Er vns </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l16">mit dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> </ab></add> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_line_1574256135171_1697">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreẏb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wollet <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> laſʒ wiſſen / <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchreib</expan> / ob Er 
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l19">auch </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> freunde </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l25">
<del rend="strikethrough">oder <expan cert="unknown">fein</expan> auch ſein wölle 
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_line_1574256184984_1714">oder niht </ab></add> / <expan>vvan<ex>n</ex></expan> wir <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ Er in lantmanſwe </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l26">
<del rend="strikethrough">vvie daʒ Er nach den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>ir<ex>er</ex></expan> habe ſtelle / des wir doch vnbe </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l28">
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſorgt vor Jm ſein </del> daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">vns </del> <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_64_r1l27">durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab></add> mit Jm auſʒtragen wöllet </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_64_r1l29">daʒ vns 
<del rend="strikethrough">C noch </del> ein <expan>antvv<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darauff werde / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_64" id="30v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Dyetrich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Hofer, pfleger czu
                                    <expan>Strawbing<ex>en</ex></expan>
</del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Lieber her pfleger, uns hat der edel, wolgeporen
                                    <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, graf Eczel von Ortemberg,
                                <add>und vicztum in Nydern Beyern</add> vormals einen brief gesant
                            und <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan> von
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Caspar Hertembergers wegen, darauff wir
                            im wider <expan>geschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, als wir euch abschrift senden verslossen
                            in disem brief. Nu ist uns biz her noch khein
                                <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darauff worden, <add>so
                                        <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                        <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie das
                                    <add>der</add>
<expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> graf Eczel <add>lange</add> niht
                                anheim sey gewesen</add> und also wissen wir niht, wie wir mit
                                    <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Caspar<ex>en</ex></expan> Hertemberg daran sein.
                                    <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, <add>wen<ex>n</ex> der vicztum
                                        <expan>heimkume<ex>n</ex></expan></add> willen <add>mit dem
                                        <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan></add>, daz ir
                                    <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan></add> mit im ausztragen wöllet, daz
                            uns ein <expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> darauff werde. Das
                                    <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</del></ab>
</div>
</div></body>
